{"id": "ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 368, "displayName": {"text": "Asanebo", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Renowned upscale restaurant serving sushi, grilled fish & other Japanese fare in unassuming digs.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0aVRERjJVMFpGYlZGT1IwdFpSRlJmZUhOd01WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My daughter took me as a surprise for my Christmas present. The food was wonderful some of the best sushi I’ve ever had. The service was impeccable and we had a wonderful time. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My daughter took me as a surprise for my Christmas present. The food was wonderful some of the best sushi I’ve ever had. The service was impeccable and we had a wonderful time. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "William Gerry", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116390351701200298374/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPBVFgiXWfKMp2CU6-YJ4ZuMcGkQ4xfUf6J0Xs868w4YC6UUjz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-29T00:10:01.351546446Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0aVRERjJVMFpGYlZGT1IwdFpSRlJmZUhOd01WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0aVRERjJVMFpGYlZGT1IwdFpSRlJmZUhOd01WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2be07e212a13b:0x4911efa3a7e2ef43"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OcFEwTlRNbDlvYW5sSlQydFNhbVZTU1ZOZmJVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They are famous on social media for their fun videos, but the owner and the staff here are true professionals who are genuinely dedicated to Japanese cuisine!\nWe visited with family and close friends to celebrate, and enjoyed a full course meal. Since I’m pregnant, they kindly prepared a special menu without raw items just for me, which I truly appreciated. It had been a long time since I last had Japanese food this delicious, and I was really touched. The creative use of ingredients like truffle and cilantro made the course exciting to enjoy all the way to the end. Not only the fish, but also carefully selected ingredients like tomatoes and Brussels sprouts were outstanding, showing their dedication to quality.\nAfter dining here, I completely understand why this place has been loved for so many years!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They are famous on social media for their fun videos, but the owner and the staff here are true professionals who are genuinely dedicated to Japanese cuisine!\nWe visited with family and close friends to celebrate, and enjoyed a full course meal. Since I’m pregnant, they kindly prepared a special menu without raw items just for me, which I truly appreciated. It had been a long time since I last had Japanese food this delicious, and I was really touched. The creative use of ingredients like truffle and cilantro made the course exciting to enjoy all the way to the end. Not only the fish, but also carefully selected ingredients like tomatoes and Brussels sprouts were outstanding, showing their dedication to quality.\nAfter dining here, I completely understand why this place has been loved for so many years!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Koko", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107944760139559783661/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6Ik6cEVPjk6WL2MHb-_BcQqXpGPth2Y6VzQg7Zd0nPuLERx8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-11T10:44:01.016891898Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OcFEwTlRNbDlvYW5sSlQydFNhbVZTU1ZOZmJVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OcFEwTlRNbDlvYW5sSlQydFNhbVZTU1ZOZmJVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2be07e212a13b:0x4911efa3a7e2ef43"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaMU1URkxlR2t5WlhOd1JtUjNjRFpmVUVkbmIxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "my wife and I came here the day after Valentines day. Service, impeccable; food, unmatched. They were 100% on top of service and it was definitely a great experience. They were nice, caring and very aware of what was going on. The food was on another level, extremely fresh, very flavorful and unique. The only negative I have is that its a small space and not much room but they did great to make sure the table doesn't get cluttered. Also, be sure to try their lava cake.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "my wife and I came here the day after Valentines day. Service, impeccable; food, unmatched. They were 100% on top of service and it was definitely a great experience. They were nice, caring and very aware of what was going on. The food was on another level, extremely fresh, very flavorful and unique. The only negative I have is that its a small space and not much room but they did great to make sure the table doesn't get cluttered. Also, be sure to try their lava cake.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mike Baharian", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107990878708495903362/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfoMKVjMvEEgTqdqPlBJxIB6jqDqyOCfEu9YxF8R5GJNcwiRVSZg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-19T04:27:01.122171076Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaMU1URkxlR2t5WlhOd1JtUjNjRFpmVUVkbmIxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaMU1URkxlR2t5WlhOd1JtUjNjRFpmVUVkbmIxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2be07e212a13b:0x4911efa3a7e2ef43"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podlJUY3plRTFYY0MxV0xYcHhhRmhDT1d4bVpHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I went for a birthday celebration and had a set sushi course. The sushi was delicious however I wouldn't say anything particularly stood out to me in terms of taste or presentation. I do remember the intro chauwanmushi and wagyu \"tacos\" were pretty good. The staff was very attentive and the energy of the room was very good. Maybe I built it up too much in my head based on reading previous reviews", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I went for a birthday celebration and had a set sushi course. The sushi was delicious however I wouldn't say anything particularly stood out to me in terms of taste or presentation. I do remember the intro chauwanmushi and wagyu \"tacos\" were pretty good. The staff was very attentive and the energy of the room was very good. Maybe I built it up too much in my head based on reading previous reviews", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Peter Babida", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100616328893787360352/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGfi77_WotsZXsRfpXiltouGK4_eIJ7Rko2ApcgVVaV533JPVQPA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-04T23:48:00.319124982Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podlJUY3plRTFYY0MxV0xYcHhhRmhDT1d4bVpHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2podlJUY3plRTFYY0MxV0xYcHhhRmhDT1d4bVpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2be07e212a13b:0x4911efa3a7e2ef43"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO6ES4ge-woARQ-_ip6PvEUk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHl